{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/Database/database-Transaction-isolation-level","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"d5c3ea3b-a0dd-5713-b9b8-187f861b4dbd","html":"<h2 id=\"개요\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%9C%EC%9A%94\" aria-label=\"개요 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>개요</h2>\n<p>SQL 트랜잭션의 격리수준을 정리중입니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"트랜잭션-격리수준이란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%8A%B8%EB%9E%9C%EC%9E%AD%EC%85%98-%EA%B2%A9%EB%A6%AC%EC%88%98%EC%A4%80%EC%9D%B4%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"트랜잭션 격리수준이란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>트랜잭션 격리수준이란?</h2>\n<p>SQL 표준에서는 트랜잭션의 <strong>동시성을 제어하기 위한 방법</strong>으로 네 종류의 트랜잭션 격리 수준을 정의하고 있다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"트랜잭션-격리-수준이-필요한-이유는\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%8A%B8%EB%9E%9C%EC%9E%AD%EC%85%98-%EA%B2%A9%EB%A6%AC-%EC%88%98%EC%A4%80%EC%9D%B4-%ED%95%84%EC%9A%94%ED%95%9C-%EC%9D%B4%EC%9C%A0%EB%8A%94\" aria-label=\"트랜잭션 격리 수준이 필요한 이유는 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>트랜잭션 격리 수준이 필요한 이유는?</h2>\n<p>데이터베이스에는 ACID라는 트랜잭션이 올바르게 처리되고 데이터가 항상 일관된 상태로 유지할 수 있도록 하는 원칙이 존재한다. 항상 일관된 상태로 데이터를 유지하기 위해서는 멀티 스레드로 돌아가는 데이터베이스의 동시성 작업에서 무조건 락을걸어서 순차적으로 제어를 한다면 데이터베이스의 성능이 낮아질 수 밖에 없다. 이에, 성능을 위해 격리 수준을 제어할 수 있는 방법이 필요하다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"트랜잭션-격리수준의-종류\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%8A%B8%EB%9E%9C%EC%9E%AD%EC%85%98-%EA%B2%A9%EB%A6%AC%EC%88%98%EC%A4%80%EC%9D%98-%EC%A2%85%EB%A5%98\" aria-label=\"트랜잭션 격리수준의 종류 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>트랜잭션 격리수준의 종류</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Read uncommitted</li>\n<li>Read committed</li>\n<li>Repeatable read</li>\n<li>Serializable</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"read-uncommitted\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#read-uncommitted\" aria-label=\"read uncommitted permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Read uncommitted</h3>\n<h3 id=\"read-committed\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#read-committed\" aria-label=\"read committed permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Read committed</h3>\n<h3 id=\"repeatable-read\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#repeatable-read\" aria-label=\"repeatable read permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Repeatable read</h3>\n<h3 id=\"serializable\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#serializable\" aria-label=\"serializable permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Serializable</h3>\n<p>가장 높은 수준의 격리수준으로 직렬화가 가능한 스냅숏 격리이다. 이 단계는 여러 세션에 있는 트랜잭션 작업들을 한번에 하나씩 진행하는 것과 같은 결과를 보장한다. 하지만, 그만큼 성능이 느려지게된다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reference</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.postgresql.org/docs/current/transaction-iso.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://www.postgresql.org/docs/current/transaction-iso.html</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://joont92.github.io/db/%ED%8A%B8%EB%9E%9C%EC%9E%AD%EC%85%98-%EA%B2%A9%EB%A6%AC-%EC%88%98%EC%A4%80-isolation-level/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://joont92.github.io/db/%ED%8A%B8%EB%9E%9C%EC%9E%AD%EC%85%98-%EA%B2%A9%EB%A6%AC-%EC%88%98%EC%A4%80-isolation-level/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://doooyeon.github.io/2018/09/29/transaction-isolation-level.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://doooyeon.github.io/2018/09/29/transaction-isolation-level.html</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/Database/database-Transaction-isolation-level","tagSlugs":["/tag/database/","/tag/isolation-level/","/tag/concurrency/","/tag/transaction/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2021-01-16T22:00:00.000Z","description":"데이터베이스 